1. create objects with css-like settings:
  new Button("Hello", "border-size: 2px; color:red;");
2. update object styles:
  buttonInst.style.override(new Style("color: green; margin-right: 10px"));
3. set pixel/percent/ size
  buttonInst.percentWidth = 100;
  buttonInst.setStyle("height: 200px");
  buttonInst.width = NaN;
  buttonInst.delStyle("width");
4. set absolute/anchor-based position:
  labelInst.x = 100;
  labelInst.align = "left";
  labelInst.valign = "botton";